{"serial": "61017", "department_serial": 54, "code": "AP4041", "class": "*", "name": {"en": "Principle of Environmental Sampling and Analysis", "ch": "環境檢測原理"}, "notice": {"en": "", "ch": ""}, "instructor": {"en": ["Sheu, Guey-Rong"], "ch": ["許桂榮"]}, "credits": 2, "time_loc": [{"time": {"week": 5, "session": ["3", "4"]}, "loc": {"building": "S1", "room": "625"}}], "isRequired": false, "isFullSem": false, "MaxStu": -1, "department": {"ch": "大氣科學學系", "en": "Department of Atmospheric Physics"}, "system": {"ch": "學士班", "en": "Undergraduate Programme"}, "language": {"ch": "國語", "en": "Chinese"}, "card": {"ch": "不使用", "en": "None"}, "assigned": 17, "selected": 0, "remark": {"ch": "", "en": ""}, "goal": {"ch": "現代人越來越注重環境品質，但各式環境污染問題仍是層出不窮，而要瞭解污染物對於環境生態以及人體健康的危害，或是要解決環境問題，需先掌握環境背景及污染現況，了解污染物在空氣、水與土壤等環境介質中的濃度、物種組成、分布及傳輸，才能據以提出合適的因應對策，因此環境檢測與分析是不可或缺的重要工具。本課程將介紹環境污染物採樣、樣品保存及前處理、分析方法、品保品管作業、儀器校正與維護，並重點說明物理與化學性的環境採樣與分析方法，如光譜分析與層析分析，以及這些方法在大氣、水、土壤與沈積物環境檢測的應用。修習此課程後，學生能具備關於環境檢測與分析之知識與技能。", "en": "\"Learn basics about sampling and analysis of environmental pollutants, including sampling plan and design, sample storage and pre-treatment, analytical methods, quality assurance and quality control, and instrument calibration and maintenance.\""}, "outline": {"ch": "\"1. 緒論\n2. 環境採樣與分析基礎\n3. 數據品質指標\n4. 採樣規劃\n5. 採樣方法\n6. 品質保證與品質管制\n7. 樣品準備與前處理\n8. 層析分析\n9. 光譜分析\n10. 超微量分析\"", "en": "\"1. Introduction to Environmental Data Acquisition\n2. Basics of Environmental Sampling and Analysis\n3. Data Quality Indicators\n4. Environmental Sampling Design\n5. Environmental Sampling Techniques\n6. Methodology and Quality Assurance/Quality Control of Environmental Analysis\n7. Sample Preparation for Environmental Analysis\n8. Chromatographic Methods for Environmental Analysis\n9. Atomic Spectroscopy for Metal Analysis\n10. Sampling and Analysis of Ultra-Trace Hg\""}, "textbook": {"ch": "\"1. 楊末雄等著，環境分析–原理與應用，環境分析學會出版，2012。 \n2. Zhang, C., Fundamentals of Environmental Sampling and Analysis, John Wiley& Sons, Inc., 2007.\n3. Reeve, R.N., Introduction to Environmental Analysis, John Wiley& Sons, Inc., 2002.\"", "en": "\"1. 楊末雄等著，環境分析–原理與應用，環境分析學會出版，2012。 \n2. Zhang, C., Fundamentals of Environmental Sampling and Analysis, John Wiley& Sons, Inc., 2007.\n3. Reeve, R.N., Introduction to Environmental Analysis, John Wiley& Sons, Inc., 2002.\""}, "selfCompiledRate": {"ch": "0", "en": "0"}, "instructMethod": {"ch": "講授\n研討\n\n\n其他", "en": ["Lecture", "Seminar", "", "", "Others"]}, "gradMethod": {"ch": "\"1. 作業、平時測驗、報告、上課情形 20-30%\n2. 期中考                         30-40%\n3. 期末考                         30-40%\"", "en": "\"1. Class Participation, report, quiz and Homework    20-30%\n2. Mid-term Exam                                           30-40%\n3. Final Exam                                       30-40%\""}, "officeHour": {"ch": "週三上午10:00-11:50及下午3:00-4:00", "en": "\"Wednesday, 10:00-11:50 am and 3:00-4:00 pm\""}, "teachWeeks": {"ch": "18", "en": "18"}, "flexDiscription": {"ch": "", "en": ""}, "domain": {"ch": "基礎學科(大氣組)\n\n\n、\n\n\n大氣環境(大氣組)", "en": "基礎學科(大氣組)\n\n\n、\n\n\n大氣環境(大氣組)"}, "map": {"ch": [{"competencies": "數理基礎能力", "rating": "(3)普通", "assesments": ["紙筆測驗/會考", "作業練習"]}, {"competencies": "專業知識能力", "rating": "(4)高", "assesments": ["紙筆測驗/會考", "作業練習"]}, {"competencies": "資訊應用能力", "rating": "(4)高", "assesments": ["紙筆測驗/會考", "作業練習"]}, {"competencies": "國際視野與語文溝通能力", "rating": "(3)普通", "assesments": ["紙筆測驗/會考", "作業練習", "出席/課堂表現"]}, {"competencies": "獨立思考能力", "rating": "(4)高", "assesments": ["紙筆測驗/會考", "作業練習", "出席/課堂表現"]}, {"competencies": "專業倫理及服務學習之能力", "rating": "(4)高", "assesments": ["出席/課堂表現"]}], "en": [{"competencies": "Ability in basic mathematics and science", "rating": "(3)Medium", "assesments": ["Test/Exam", "Assignments"]}, {"competencies": "Ability in professional knowledge", "rating": "(4)High", "assesments": ["Test/Exam", "Assignments"]}, {"competencies": "Ability in information applications", "rating": "(4)High", "assesments": ["Test/Exam", "Assignmen